%N A393345 Irregular triangle read by rows: T(n,k) is the number of connected graphs on n nodes with genus k, 0 <= k <= A000933(n).
%C A393345 T(n,0) = A003094(n).
%C A393345 T(n,1) = A319115(n).
%C A393345 Sum_{k=0..A000933(n)} T(n,k) = A001349(n).
%C A393345 The length of row n is A000933(n)+1.
